001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.BaseSubProjectionNode;
004import java.lang.String;
005import java.util.ArrayList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008public class AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {
009  public AttributeDefinitionProjection(PARENT parent, ROOT root) {
010    super(parent, root, java.util.Optional.of("AttributeDefinition"));
011  }
012
013  public AttributeDefinitionTypeProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> type(
014      ) {
015     AttributeDefinitionTypeProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new AttributeDefinitionTypeProjection<>(this, getRoot());
016     getFields().put("type", projection);
017     return projection;
018  }
019
020  public AttributeConstraintProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> attributeConstraint(
021      ) {
022     AttributeConstraintProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new AttributeConstraintProjection<>(this, getRoot());
023     getFields().put("attributeConstraint", projection);
024     return projection;
025  }
026
027  public TextInputHintProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> inputHint() {
028     TextInputHintProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new TextInputHintProjection<>(this, getRoot());
029     getFields().put("inputHint", projection);
030     return projection;
031  }
032
033  public LocalizedStringProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> labelAllLocales(
034      ) {
035     LocalizedStringProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new LocalizedStringProjection<>(this, getRoot());
036     getFields().put("labelAllLocales", projection);
037     return projection;
038  }
039
040  public LocalizedStringProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> inputTipAllLocales(
041      ) {
042     LocalizedStringProjection<AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new LocalizedStringProjection<>(this, getRoot());
043     getFields().put("inputTipAllLocales", projection);
044     return projection;
045  }
046
047  public AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT> name() {
048    getFields().put("name", null);
049    return this;
050  }
051
052  public AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT> label() {
053    getFields().put("label", null);
054    return this;
055  }
056
057  public AttributeDefinitionProjection label(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
058    getFields().put("label", null);
059    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("label", k -> new ArrayList<>());
060    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
061    getInputArguments().get("label").add(localeArg);
062    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
063    getInputArguments().get("label").add(acceptLanguageArg);
064    return this;
065  }
066
067  public AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT> isRequired() {
068    getFields().put("isRequired", null);
069    return this;
070  }
071
072  public AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT> inputTip() {
073    getFields().put("inputTip", null);
074    return this;
075  }
076
077  public AttributeDefinitionProjection inputTip(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
078    getFields().put("inputTip", null);
079    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("inputTip", k -> new ArrayList<>());
080    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
081    getInputArguments().get("inputTip").add(localeArg);
082    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
083    getInputArguments().get("inputTip").add(acceptLanguageArg);
084    return this;
085  }
086
087  public AttributeDefinitionProjection<PARENT, ROOT> isSearchable() {
088    getFields().put("isSearchable", null);
